snippet.title: PlayStation - Simple 1500 Series Vol 014 - The Block Kuzushi (1999)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
Block Kuzushi is an Action game, developed by Tamsoft and published by Karuchua, which was released in Japan in 1999.
